Iconic Luminaires are instantly recognisable in the lighting world. As a proudly Czechia based manufacturer, we pay homage to the past, bringing you a new icon, the SVOPATT™.
Transforming into the modern age, you cannot fail to make an impact with the SVOPATT™ both as a scenic element and a source of captivating effects. With nine individual modules each containing 7 x 40W RGBW multichips and the centre pixel also containing a 200W white LED strobe, the fixture generates over 75.000 lm (integrating sphere). You have a source worthy of its lineage.
